 <item> <title>Early Learning Initiative</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/early-learning-old</link>
 <description>President Obama is committed to providing the support that our youngest children need to succeed later in school. The importance of the early years in a child&#039;s life has been well documented. The Department of Education (ED) prioritizes improving the health, social, emotional, and educational outcomes for young children from birth through 3rd grade by: 

enhancing the quality of early learning programs, and 
increasing the access to high quality early learning programs especially for young children at risk for school failure. 

</description>
 <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ed.gov/early-learning-old</guid>
